Cable Says U.K. on Target to Erase Structural Deficit by 2015

-- B y   A n d r e w   A t k i n s o n
-- 
2011-09-21T12:11:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/cable-says-u-k-on-target-to-erase-structural-deficit-by-2015.html
Business Secretary Vince Cable said
the government is sticking to its deficit-reduction program,
saying Britain is on course to erase the structural shortfall
during the current parliament.  Cable said in an interview with  Sky News  that August’s
higher-than-forecast borrowing reported today was a “warning”
for the government to keep to its plans.  To contact the reporter on this story:
